metadata.name: Uprise
metadata.description:
The most important piece of this collection.

Meet your inner Warrior. You can't see his face. But  you can feel his power. 

You are one. You and him. You can even remember the day you met each other. Remember that cold time? When you were the loneliest man on Earth, bleedeng with your head on the ground, crying inside and begging for the end of this anguish, no matter how. 

'Course you do. You'll never forget. That was the day your Inner Warrior uprised. And now you both rule this world.
